      "content": "i know i should check with my doctor but i cant get an appointment until next week and i'm miserable right now. i've read online that it helps with the pressure and i've taken it before without any issues. is there a specific dose that’s definitely safe, or like, is it actually dangerous if i just take one or two to get through the night?",
